FBIS3-17500 "drsov059_r_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-059 Document Type:Daily Report 26 Mar 1994 Azerbaijan Reopening of Armenian AES Seen as `Real Threat' LD2603103694 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0800 GMT 26 Mar 94 LD2603103694 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] People in Azerbaijan are concerned at the report that preparations are under way to reopen the Armenian nuclear power station. A statement of the Azerbaijani president's press service says that recommissioning putting the AES [nuclear electric power station] in a country that is conducting active combat operations against Azerbaijan involving the use of the latest weapons represents a real threat to the safety of the countries of the region.
